  <h>faic</h>
  <p><g>faic</g>
    <en>see</en> is an irregular verb.</p>
  <section id="forms">
    <h>forms</h>
    <p>The principal parts of <g>faic</g> are – <ul>
        <li><m>chì</m> – future independent, i.e. <en>will see</en></li>
        <li><m>chunnaic</m> – past independent, i.e. <en>saw</en></li>
        <li><m>faicinn</m> – verbal noun, i.e. <en>seeing</en></li>
      </ul>
    </p>
