                  <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhaca</m>, am <m>faca</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>chunnacas</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>chunnacas</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhacas</m>, am <m>facas</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>future <ul id="future">
              <li>active <ul>
                  <li>independent – <m>chì</m></li>
                  <li>relative – a <m>chì</m></li>
                  <li>dependent – chan/nach <m>fhaic</m>, am <m>faic</m></li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>passive <ul>
